ed="T" n="0820c13"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0820c13"/><head><date from-iso="+0557-11-18" key="j19248221936231" to-iso="+0589-02-12">陳</date><placeName key="PL000000048606">新羅國</placeName><persName key="A012070">玄光</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0820c14"/><persName key="A012070">釋玄光</persName>者，海東<placeName key="PL000000048614">熊州</placeName>人也。少而頴悟，頓厭俗<lb
ed="T" n="0820c15"/>塵，決求名師，專修<name>梵</name>行。迨夫成長，願越滄<lb
ed="T" n="0820c16"/>溟，求<placeName key="PL000000000083">中土</placeName>禪法。於是觀光<placeName key="PL000000000074">陳國</placeName>，利往<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡山</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0820c17"/>見<persName key="A001711">思<roleName>大和尚</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n2306"/>，開物成化<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1232"/>，神解相參。<persName key="A001711">思<roleName>師</roleName></persName>察<lb
ed="T" n="0820c18"/>其所由，密授《法華安樂行門》<ptr target="#n2304"/>。<persName key="A012070">光</persName>利若神錐，<lb
ed="T" n="0820c19"/>無堅不犯；新猶劫貝<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1235"/>，有染皆鮮。稟而奉行，<lb
ed="T" n="0820c20"/>勤而罔忒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1239"/>，俄證法華三昧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g178"/>，請求印可。<persName key="A001711">思</persName>為<lb
ed="T" n="0820c21"/>證之：「<ref type="person" target="#A012070">汝</ref>之所證，真實不虛，善護念之，令法<lb
ed="T" n="0820c22"/>增長。<ref type="person" target="#A012070">汝</ref>還本土，施設善權，好負螟蛉，皆成<lb
ed="T" n="0820c23"/>蜾蠃。<ptr target="#n2305"/>」<persName key="A012070">光</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0820sgsz16"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0820sgsz16"/>而垂泣，自爾返錫<placeName key="PL000000000197">江南</placeName>。屬本國<lb
ed="T" n="0820c24"/>舟艦附載，離岸時，則綵雲亂目，雅樂沸空，<lb
ed="T" n="0820c25"/>絳節霓旌，傳呼而至。空中聲云：「<persName key="A002869">天帝</persName>召<ref type="place" target="#PL000000048606">海東</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0820c26"/><persName key="A012070">玄光<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>。」<persName key="A012070">光</persName>拱手避讓，唯見青衣前導，少<lb
ed="T" n="0820c27"/>選入宮城，且非人間官府。羽衛之設也，無<lb
ed="T" n="0820c28"/>非鱗介，參雜鬼神。或曰：「今日<persName key="A002869">天帝</persName>降<placeName key="PL000000055445">龍王<lb
ed="T" n="0820c29"/>宮</placeName>，請<ref type="person" target="#A012070">師</ref>說親證法門，吾曹水府，蒙<ref type="person" target="#A012070">師</ref>利益。」<pb ed="T" n="0821a" xml:id="T50.2061.0821a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0821a01"/>既登寶殿，次陟高臺，如問而談，略經七日。<lb
ed="T" n="0821a02"/>然後王躬送別，其船泛洋不進。<persName key="A012070">光</persName>復登船，<lb
ed="T" n="0821a03"/>船人謂經半日而已。<persName key="A012070">光</persName>歸<placeName key="PL000000048615"><placeName>熊州</placeName><placeName>翁山</placeName></placeName>，卓錫<lb
ed="T" n="0821a04"/>結茅，乃成<name>梵</name>剎。同聲相應，得法者蟄戶爰<lb
ed="T" n="0821a05"/>開；樂小迴心<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1249"/>，慕羶者螘連倏至<ptr type="glossary" target="#g931"/>。其如升堂<lb
ed="T" n="0821a06"/>受莂者一人<ptr target="#n2307"/>，入火光三昧一人，入水光三<lb
ed="T" n="0821a07"/>昧二人<ptr target="#n2308"/>，互得其二種法門<ptr target="#n2309"/>。從發者彰三昧<lb
ed="T" n="0821a08"/>名耳。其諸門生，譬如眾鳥附<placeName key="PL000000055454">須彌山</placeName>，皆同<lb
ed="T" n="0821a09"/>一色也<ptr target="#n2310"/>。<persName key="A012070">光</persName>末之滅，罔知攸往。<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>祖構<lb
ed="T" n="0821a10"/>影堂，內圖二十八人，<persName key="A012070">光</persName>居一焉。<placeName key="PL000000014664"><placeName>天台</placeName><placeName>國清<lb
ed="T" n="0821a11"/>寺</placeName></placeName>祖堂亦然。</p>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0821a1201"><lb
ed="T" n="0821a12"/>系曰：夫約佛滅後，驗入道之人，以教、理、行、<lb
ed="T" n="0821a13"/>果<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1240"/>四法明之，則無逃隱矣！去聖彌近者，修<lb
ed="T" n="0821a14"/>行成果位證也。去聖稍遙者，學教易見理<lb
ed="T" n="0821a15"/>親也。其更綿邈者，學教不精，見理非諦。夫<lb
ed="T" n="0821a16"/>一念不生，前後際斷，斯頓心成佛也<ptr target="#n2311"/>。理佛具<lb
ed="T" n="0821a17"/>足行布<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1215"/>、<anchor xml:id="beg0821001"/>施<anchor xml:id="end0821001"/>行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1244"/>，曾未嘗述行佛<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1241"/>。具體而微：<lb
ed="T" n="0821a18"/><placeName key="PL000000000083">東夏</placeName>自<persName key="A001719">六祖</persName>已來，多談禪理，少談禪行<lb
ed="T" n="0821a19"/>焉。非<persName key="A001719">南能</persName>不說行，且令見道如救<anchor xml:id="beg0821002"/>頭<anchor xml:id="end0821002"/>然<lb
ed="T" n="0821a20"/>之故<ptr target="#n2312"/>。<placeName key="PL000000028928">南岳</placeName><persName key="A001711">思<roleName>師</roleName></persName>切在兼修，乘戒俱急<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1180"/>，是以學<lb
ed="T" n="0821a21"/>者驗諸行果<ptr type="glossary" target="#g992"/>。其如入火光三昧者，《處胎經》<ptr target="#n2313"/><lb
ed="T" n="0821a22"/>中以禪定攝意入火界三昧，剎土洞然。愚<lb
ed="T" n="0821a23"/>夫謂是遭焚。若入水界三昧，愚夫見謂為<lb
ed="T" n="0821a24"/>水，投物于中。菩薩心如虛空不覺觸嬈者<ptr target="#n2314"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0821a25"/>此非二乘<ptr type="glossary" target="#g855"/>所能究盡也。斯乃急於行果焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0821a26"/>無令口說而身意不修，何由助道<anchor xml:id="beg0821sgsz2"/>耶<anchor xml:id="end0821sgsz2"/>？</p>
